fields.title: Standard Time podcast S1E24
fields.description:
The #EU likes to promote its devotion to human rights, but you  won’t need a magnifying glass to see that this agenda falls short when  it comes to #border regimes, #migration and especially, non-European  #refugees.
Our guests are Sedra Arab, Gustavo de la Orden Bosch, and Philipp  Ther #borders #migration #EU #EUSecurity #Security #ForeignPolicy  #refugees #history #EuropeanHistory #immigration #asylum #EPElections  #racism #anti-racism #humanrights #MigrationPact
Standard Time, Eurozine’s weekly talk show is a Display Europe  production, offering thoughtful conversations on topics with a  cross-European interest. Make sure to subscribe to our channel to watch our latest episodes
